Class Function

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kohsuke.stapler.Function
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ForwardingFunction

    public abstract class Function
extends Object
    Abstracts the difference between normal instance methods and static duck-typed methods.
    Author:
    Kohsuke Kawaguchi
